<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>García Mobiliario</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

:root{
--negro:#1a1a1a;
--gris:#444;
--tarjeta:#ffffff;
}

/* RESET */

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Montserrat,sans-serif;
}

/* MESA DE MADERA REALISTA */

body{

background-color:#8b5a2b;

background-image:

/* vetas largas */
repeating-linear-gradient(
90deg,
rgba(60,35,20,0.35) 0px,
rgba(60,35,20,0.35) 2px,
transparent 2px,
transparent 8px
),

/* vetas secundarias */
repeating-linear-gradient(
90deg,
rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 0px,
rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 1px,
transparent 1px,
transparent 4px
),

/* color base */
linear-gradient(
90deg,
#6e4527,
#8b5a2b,
#7a4a2a,
#8b5a2b
);

background-size:100% 100%,100% 100%,cover;

min-height:100vh;

display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
align-items:center;

padding:40px 20px;

}

/* CONTENEDOR */

.container{

max-width:600px;
width:100%;

display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
gap:25px;

}

/* TARJETAS */

.card{

background:var(--tarjeta);

border-radius:16px;

padding:30px;

box-shadow:

0 25px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.35),
0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);

animation:entrada .8s ease;

}

/* ANIMACIÓN SUAVE */

@keyframes entrada{

from{
opacity:0;
transform:translateY(40px);
}

to{
opacity:1;
transform:translateY(0);
}

}

/* LOGO */

.logo{

height:150px;
display:block;
margin:auto;

mix-blend-mode:multiply;

}

/* TITULOS */

.title{

font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;

text-align:center;

font-size:2rem;

color:var(--negro);

margin-top:10px;

}

.subtitle{

text-align:center;

font-size:.95rem;

color:var(--gris);

margin-top:5px;

}

/* BOTONES */

.social{

display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
gap:12px;

margin-top:20px;

}

.btn{

padding:14px;

text-align:center;

border-radius:8px;

text-decoration:none;

font-weight:700;

border:2px solid var(--negro);

color:var(--negro);

transition:.25s;

}

.btn:hover{

background:var(--negro);
color:white;

}

/* VIDEO */

.video-container{

margin-top:15px;

border-radius:14px;

overflow:hidden;

aspect-ratio:9/16;

}

.video-container iframe{

width:100%;
height:100%;
border:none;

}

/* HORARIO */

.schedule-title{

font-weight:700;

margin-bottom:15px;

border-bottom:2px solid #8b5a2b;

display:inline-block;

padding-bottom:5px;

}

.schedule{

display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;

font-weight:600;

margin-bottom:8px;

}

/* ACORDEON */

.accordion-btn{

width:100%;

background:none;

border:none;

padding:15px 0;

font-weight:700;

cursor:pointer;

display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;

border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.15);

}

.accordion-content{

max-height:0;

overflow:hidden;

transition:max-height .3s ease;

font-size:.9rem;

}

.accordion-content p{

padding:10px 0;

}

/* FOOTER */

footer{

margin-top:25px;

color:white;

text-align:center;

font-size:.85rem;

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<!-- LOGO -->

<div class="card">

<img src="https://cdn.phototourl.com/uploads/2026-03-11-40763071-6990-49a9-9f1b-23ece2653c87.png" class="logo">

<h1 class="title">GARCÍA MOBILIARIO</h1>

<p class="subtitle">Arte en cada corte, pasión en cada proyecto</p>

</div>

<!-- REDES -->

<div class="card">

<h3 class="schedule-title">Nuestros Canales</h3>

<div class="social">

<a class="btn"
href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=573193384549"
target="_blank">Cotizar por WhatsApp</a>

<a class="btn"
href="https://www.instagram.com/garciamobiliario__"
target="_blank">Instagram</a>

<a class="btn"
href="https://www.facebook.com/share/1GiYH96ikN/"
target="_blank">Facebook</a>

<a class="btn"
href="https://www.tiktok.com/@garciamobiliario"
target="_blank">TikTok</a>

</div>

</div>

<!-- VIDEO -->

<div class="card">

<h3 class="schedule-title">Nuestro Trabajo</h3>

<div class="video-container">

<iframe
src="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DBZFUR4RPc-/embed"
allow="autoplay">
</iframe>

</div>

</div>

<!-- HORARIO -->

<div class="card">

<h3 class="schedule-title">Horario de Atención</h3>

<div class="schedule">
<span>Lunes a Viernes</span>
<span>8 AM - 6 PM</span>
</div>

<div class="schedule">
<span>Sábados</span>
<span>8 AM - 1 PM</span>
</div>

</div>

<!-- GARANTÍA -->

<div class="card">

<h3 class="schedule-title">Garantía de Calidad</h3>

<button class="accordion-btn">
Materiales y Acabados <span>+</span>
</button>

<div class="accordion-content">
<p>Seleccionamos maderas de alta calidad y realizamos acabados artesanales para garantizar durabilidad y elegancia.</p>
</div>

<button class="accordion-btn">
Precisión Técnica <span>+</span>
</button>

<div class="accordion-content">
<p>Cada corte y ensamblaje es supervisado cuidadosamente para asegurar máxima precisión.</p>
</div>

<button class="accordion-btn">
Proceso de Fabricación <span>+</span>
</button>

<div class="accordion-content">
<p>Desde la materia prima hasta la entrega final, cada etapa del proceso es controlada por especialistas.</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

<footer>

<p>Barrio Villabel — Floridablanca</p>

<p>© <span id="year"></span> García Mobiliario</p>

</footer>

<script>

/* AÑO AUTOMÁTICO */

document.getElementById("year").textContent=new Date().getFullYear();

/* ACORDEON */

document.querySelectorAll(".accordion-btn").forEach(btn=>{

btn.onclick=()=>{

let panel=btn.nextElementSibling;

if(panel.style.maxHeight){

panel.style.maxHeight=null;
btn.querySelector("span").textContent="+";

}else{

panel.style.maxHeight=panel.scrollHeight+"px";
btn.querySelector("span").textContent="−";

}

}

});

</script>

</body>
</html>
